Terry,<br>
     Glad to hear your job is intact.  The Naval Command I work for has shed a 1000 jobs in 10 years, fortunately through attrition.  We have about 1750 now, and they're talking about another possible 30% cut.  I'll make it to age 55 w/30 years.  The people I worry about have between 10 &amp; 20 years under age 50.  They can't retire, but have a lot of time invested in federal service.<br>
    
